moves.name: Power Nap
moves.description: Take a short nap to regain some health. But who knows when you will wake up!

moves.name: Lecture
moves.description: Put the enemy to sleep with a long lecture!

moves.name: Shotgun Beer
moves.description: Slam a beer to get back some fast health, hope you arent a light weight... that would be embarassing.

moves.name: Pantsing
moves.description: Embarass your opponent by pantsing them in front of their friends. Hope they are wearing underwear...

moves.name: Caffeine Pills
moves.description: Get some HP back so you can stay up to cram for a final. Just careful you don't overdo it!

moves.name: Thunderous Toot
moves.description: Let out a ripping goodone and make sure to check your underwear after. Will probably make the enemy gag.

moves.name: Hit by UW Bus
moves.description: Why would you want this? Don't pick this move. Fo not pass go, do not collect 200 dollars, do not collect free tuition.

moves.name: Moon
moves.description: Blinded by a bright pale moon, the enemy might not be able to move!

moves.name: All Night Bender
moves.description: Drink all night and get some health back! You might get confused and wake up in a random cornfield though..

moves.name: Use Science
moves.description: People don't think it be like it is, but it doo. Does no damage, but a chance to confuse the Enemy.

moves.name: Punch
moves.description: Really? You want this lame move?

moves.name: Kick
moves.description: Wow, another lame attack..

moves.name: Bandage
moves.description: Not a very big bandage... but I guess it might help a little bit.

moves.name: Steroids
moves.description: Shoot enemy up with steroids! Benefits are temporary!

moves.name: Tranquilizer
moves.description: It's sleepy time for that jerk!

moves.name: Give a Jacket
moves.description: It's chilly outside, they might catch a cold!

moves.name: Join the NFL
moves.description: Sure the money's good, but this will have a lasting impact!

moves.name: Butt Stuff
moves.description: Maybe it feels good? They'll never be the same.

moves.name: Splash
moves.description: That'll show them!

moves.name: Aid the Enemy
moves.description: Apply first aid to your enemy, this confuses them!

moves.name: Smack Yourself
moves.description: Stop Hitting Yourself!!

moves.name: Surprise Exam!
moves.description: You inform the enemy of a exam they forgot to study for!

moves.name: Disappointed Father
moves.description: What are these, grades for ants?!

moves.name: Dorm Food
moves.description: You feed your foe some food from Gordons.

moves.name: Daylight
moves.description: You step outside for the first time in years!

moves.name: Thanksgiving Break
moves.description: So much turkey... can't move.

moves.name: Finals
moves.description: Its time.
